Metadata.Title: Massacre In The Morgue
Metadata.Description: Wake the fuck up samurai... We've got bodies to burn. Get out of the stretcher, get the motorcyclist suit, massacre the people in the morgue with the tanto silently.Destroy the security system, incinerate the bodies, then escape on the snowmobile, all within the time frame.Do not get spotted, and make sure no bodies are found.Good Luck, 47- You're on the clock...
